4Geeks Academy offers a course titled "Become a AI Machine Learning Engineer". This course is designed for individuals with no previous knowledge in the field and aims to help them start a career as a data scientist and build their first machine learning models. The course duration is 16 weeks, with 3 classes held weekly. The class size is limited to 12 people. The course covers topics such as Python, SQL, Looker (Google Data Studio), Streamlit, and Statistics. Participants will learn to create predictive models using Python libraries like Pandas and Numpy, and explore algorithms like Close Neighbors and Decision Trees. The course also focuses on practicing real-life case studies and using industry-standard tools. No previous experience is required, and participants can choose between English and Spanish for the syllabus and content. Certificates from the course are recognized by multiple organizations. For more information, visit the website: https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning. stop